<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>TalentX</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;
background:#000;
color:#fff;
}

.container{
max-width:850px;
margin:auto;
padding:140px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

h1{
font-size:56px;
margin-bottom:10px;
letter-spacing:-1px;
}

.tagline{
font-size:20px;
margin-bottom:40px;
color:#ccc;
}

.highlight{
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
border:2px solid #fff;
display:inline-block;
padding:12px 20px;
margin-bottom:40px;
}

.description{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.7;
max-width:700px;
margin:auto;
margin-bottom:50px;
color:#e5e5e5;
}

.button{
display:inline-block;
padding:16px 32px;
font-size:18px;
font-weight:bold;
text-decoration:none;
background:#fff;
color:#000;
border-radius:4px;
transition:0.2s;
}

.button:hover{
background:#e5e5e5;
}

footer{
margin-top:80px;
font-size:14px;
color:#888;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>TalentX</h1>

<div class="tagline">
Where compliance professionals get discovered
</div>

<div class="highlight">
Secure Interviews in 48 Hours.
</div>

<div class="description">

A platform built for <b>AML, KYC, Risk, and Compliance professionals</b>.

<br><br>

TalentX makes it easy for professionals across <b>Singapore and Malaysia</b> to create a profile, get listed, and attract opportunities from companies actively hiring compliance talent.

<br><br>

Join the early waitlist and be among the <b>first professionals featured on the platform</b>.

</div>

<a class="button" href="https://tally.so/r/D4VGWb" target="_blank">
Join the TalentX Waitlist
</a>

<footer>© 2026 TalentX<br><br>
<a href="privacy.html" style="color:#888;">Privacy Policy</a>
</footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
